title: Annual performance of the Dow Jones Composite Index 2000 to 2019
summary: In general Index value in points has rose over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2016 and 2017.
Maximum Index value in points, about 8310.35 was reported at Year 2017
The lowest Index value in points, of value 3086.07 was reported at Year 2008
